Package: ASPENGLMS
Type: Package
Title: Beta-Binomial GLMMs for Allelic Imbalance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "ASPEN", family = "GLMS Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "todo@example.com"))
Description: Helpers for fitting beta-binomial generalized linear mixed models
    to allelic counts stored in SingleCellExperiment objects, with empirical
    Bayes shrinkage and reproducible pipelines inspired by the ASPEN project.
